Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The subtitles of this video are generated by machine translation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Brevin they disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.91,0:00:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Same as before when we were teleported to Yuanyuan Paradise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.70,0:00:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you go this time
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.27,0:00:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The annoying expansion knight has disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.24,0:00:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The fortress is now ours
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.29,0:00:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the world is also ours
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.39,0:00:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't want to go so well
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.53,0:00:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,because I
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.08,0:00:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Also expand the knight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ON
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Connect these two ties across the distant time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Encounter the energy of miracles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.86,0:01:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Find more exclamations than the future depicted
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.70,0:01:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the glory with you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of the difficulties ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely must leap over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Can think like this
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.01,0:01:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s because I care about this important world and my friends
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.93,0:01:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out, refactor now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.35,0:01:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Guard you who gave me courage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe in your own power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times I have to try
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:01:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Although important things are always changing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.03,0:02:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But i will never run away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Swear to the core
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on go
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The end of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark thread
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:04:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A little stronger, black knight
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think you can be what you want
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help you Xuan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Beni
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Go Beneta
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Two traitors get together
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.41,0:04:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, give you both sanctions and real terror
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with Mr. White
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.56,0:04:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Sliga and the others showed up near Beham Tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, there is a deblocking device on the Beham Tower
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.71,0:04:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It is precisely because of this device that the earth can survive being completely cubed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sligar and the others are probably aiming for this
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If the device is destroyed, will the earth be completely cubed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:04:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Planet Rubik's Cube is still in crisis
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How to do
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.27,0:05:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Beham Tower
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be bad if the earth was cubed
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good soldiers are divided into two ways
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Qinglan and I go to Behamta
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,it is good
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Middle yellow and ten grass go to planet Rubik's Cube
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.95,0:05:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,it is good
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,hurry up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.89,0:05:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is going on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The portal is not working
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.76,0:05:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No reaction at all
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How could this be
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe because when we came back
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.00,0:05:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Was forcibly teleported back
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So there is a problem with the flow of unfolding energy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What to do with red lotus
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,no way
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know when I can teleport. It’s a waste of time to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to Beham Tower together
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.55,0:05:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,it is good
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The defense is very solid
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Same as i thought
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I’m afraid it’s helped by the unfolding energy emitted here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can the earth delay the spread of cubes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's do it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. White?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.90,0:06:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Blenox they have entered Beham Tower
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all together
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.90,0:06:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to split the troops
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,One of them went all the way to the planet Rubik’s cube and found that it couldn’t go
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don’t know but everyone is rushing to Behamta together
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need the power of the four of you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. White
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.63,0:06:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You said Beham Tower prevented the earth from becoming cubed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:07:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, the tower will extract the unfolding energy of the earth for purification
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And then spread into the atmosphere
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What a great Mr. White. Did you do it alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No one helps me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone to assist?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Our other companion
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I'll go to the portal room to assist you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,To understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please contact me when you get into the tower
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it is good
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a trap
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak earlier
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, Lord Villius is called every day
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:08:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This kind of thing burns the circuit and it is useless
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.15,0:08:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What you said is true
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I go first
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi wait
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,red lotus
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are in the elevator
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You go up the elevator first, and then you stay on the first floor
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.75,0:08:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why only i stay
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain to you later
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Qinglan listen to Mr. White's command
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,okay, I get it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.72,0:08:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone moves fast
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do when we get on the elevator
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.39,0:08:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, listen up
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Although the deblocking device is fine
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But due to Sliga and their invasion
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire system of the tower is abnormal
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.01,0:08:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Explain well, Mr. White
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, the beginning of the earth is cubed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Terrible
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I can fix the system
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But the system needs to be restarted
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.66,0:09:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So you need to use the power of the blocks in the four blocks inside the tower
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Qinglan, go to the building block room on the first floor
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.52,0:09:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I'm going
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But it’s useless to start Qinglan yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The mechanism in this room needs four people to use together to start
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.41,0:09:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,what
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Next is Zhonghuang
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.78,0:09:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh be careful
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.57,0:09:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,please
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is that device?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:09:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Lie
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,there's noise
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,hurry up
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how you stand on tiptoe, the elevator won't accelerate
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My pleasure
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.76,0:10:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh My God
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this the second knight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here to catch you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Red lotus portal device
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it in yellow
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Running around and annoying
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,it is good
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You bugs
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.53,0:12:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do some useless resistance, I can't spare you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to be evenly matched over there
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If this continues...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Use some energy to expand
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The matter is no more
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.78,0:13:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he going to do
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept the unfolding energy of evil
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, dyed in evil colors
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.76,0:13:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,what
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.29,0:13:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shan Shenlong was taken away
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The ink cloud covers the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the legend true...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.96,0:14:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the good dragon has become my servant
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Expanding the fortress is mine
