Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.19,0:14:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. White
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I stop the elevator now
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you guys…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,hurry up
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do i stay here
