Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and many more
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten grass sliga, let me introduce it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it to you here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Um leave it to me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and many more
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there only Guren left?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone back
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.29,0:15:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn those guys
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.76,0:15:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah you are
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Blenox
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.47,0:15:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dolibidon
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,hateful
