Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Block R35 blocking wall
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you Mr. White
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
