Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:15:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. White
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Are all okay
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
